since she was a small child.

54
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,733
She attended nursing school,

55
00:02:42,832 --> 00:02:46,133
and, when a high school classmate
was killed during Tet,

56
00:02:46,233 --> 00:02:50,500
joined the Army to do what
she could for the wounded.

57
00:02:51,932 --> 00:02:55,699
Furey was assigned to the
71st Evacuation Hospital

58
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:59,466
at Pleiku, in the heart
of the Central Highlands.

59
00:03:01,066 --> 00:03:04,633
Nothing had prepared her
for what she saw and did

60
00:03:04,733 --> 00:03:07,000
over the next 12 months.

61
00:03:07,099 --> 00:03:08,633
(indistinct chatter)

62
00:03:09,765 --> 00:03:10,966
(grunts)

63
00:03:11,066 --> 00:03:13,233
Wounded men were choppered in

64
00:03:13,332 --> 00:03:16,000
at all times of the day and night.

65
00:03:16,099 --> 00:03:19,066
So were Viet Cong and NVA soldiers,

66
00:03:19,165 --> 00:03:22,133
who sometimes spat at the medical personnel

67
00:03:22,233 --> 00:03:25,900
trying to save their limbs or lives.

68
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:29,066
(explosions)

69
