Whenever the hospital
came under mortar fire,

70
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:35,400
Furey stayed with the most
seriously wounded men

71
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,733
in the ICU.

72
00:03:36,832 --> 00:03:38,566
(distant explosions)

73
