00:30:37,633 --> 00:30:38,732
McDONALD: Give me a "C"!

542
00:30:38,833 --> 00:30:40,700
"C"! Give me a "K"!

543
00:30:40,799 --> 00:30:41,700
"K"!

544
00:30:41,799 --> 00:30:43,032
What's that spell?!

545
00:30:43,133 --> 00:30:45,032
NARRATOR: Two days after the battle

546
00:30:45,133 --> 00:30:47,299
in which Tom Vallely distinguished himself,

547
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,099
and while half a million Americans

548
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:51,500
were still in Vietnam,

549
00:30:51,599 --> 00:30:53,500
half a million Americans gathered

550
00:30:53,599 --> 00:30:56,465
on a dairy farm in upstate New York

551
00:30:56,566 --> 00:30:59,766
for a music festival: Woodstock.

